OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,FA Belfast-based peace-builder says it
OL,7,Fis a "great blessing" that he is able
OL,8,Fto fly to Rome to say "goodbye with
OL,9,Fmuch gratitude" at the funeral of Pope
OL,10,FFrancis.
OL,12,FEd Peterson is a lay-person who has
OL,13,Fbeen working in peace ministry at
OL,14,FClonard Monastery in west Belfast for
OL,15,Ftwo decades, and he has found the
OL,16,Fpapacy of Pope Francis inspirational.
