OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,F"I'm just so grateful that I'll have
OL,7,Fthis opportunity to go to Rome to say
OL,8,Fthat final goodbye with much gratitude
OL,9,Fto Pope Francis for his life and the
OL,10,Fimpact he has had on me and my family
OL,11,Fand my work here in Clonard," said Ed.
OL,13,FHuge crowds are expected at the
OL,14,Foutdoor mass at 10am local time on
OL,15,FSaturday, which will be presided over
OL,16,Fby Cardinal Giovanni Battista Re, who
OL,17,Fis the dean of the College of
OL,18,FCardinals.
