OL,6,FFrancis was a guiding light to Ed
OL,7,Fbecause a focus of his papacy was
OL,8,Faround work with other denominations,
OL,9,Fwhich very much aligns with Ed's job
OL,10,Fwith the Redemptorist order. They are
OL,11,Fa Catholic order founded by St.
OL,12,FAlphonsus Maria de Liguori who wanted
OL,13,Fto help the 'most abandoned souls.'
