OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,F"Both his desire for the unity of
OL,7,FChristians and that work across all
OL,8,Fdenominations of the church spoke to
OL,9,Fus very much here in Clonard, as well
OL,10,Fas his interfaith work and his
OL,11,Ffriendships that he had, whether it be
OL,12,Fmembers of the Jewish community, the
OL,13,FMuslim community.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
