OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,F"Probably for me his most
OL,7,Finspirational writing was something
OL,8,Fcalled Fratelli Tutti, which is the
OL,9,FItalian title of an encyclical that
OL,10,Fwas basically saying that we are all
OL,11,Fsisters and brothers, and that began
OL,12,Fwith a relationship that he had with
OL,13,Fthe Muslim sultan and the friendship
OL,14,Fthat they built and just about our
OL,15,Fcommon humanity.
OL,17,F"And it wasn't something that was
OL,18,Fwritten just for Catholics or even
OL,19,Fjust for Christians.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
