OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,F"Pope Francis always seemed to have a
OL,7,Fwider vision that everybody was part
OL,8,Fof this, human family together and
OL,9,Falbeit he did that within his own
OL,10,FCatholic Jesuit context, but he wanted
OL,11,Feveryone to feel part of this family
OL,12,Ftogether that he felt part of, whether
OL,13,Fthey were from a particular religious
OL,14,Fviewpoint or faith viewpoint or or
OL,15,Fthose maybe who are even humanists,
OL,16,Fatheists all I think would have felt a
OL,17,Fplace at the table with Pope Francis."
OL,19,FHaving met his wife in Rome, the
OL,20,FEternal City is a special place for
OL,21,Fthe Petersons.
