OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,FThey would have loved to have made the
OL,7,Fpilgrimage back together, but he said
OL,8,Fshe has taken one for the team and is
OL,9,Fstaying at home in Belfast so that he
OL,10,Fcan go.
OL,12,F"I immediately was hopeful that maybe
OL,13,FI could make it over, and I'm just so
OL,14,Fgrateful that everything has worked
OL,15,Fout and that I will get to be there."
