OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,FBy Thursday lunchtime, more than
OL,7,F60,000 people had stood in line for
OL,8,Fhours in St Peter's Square to make
OL,9,Ftheir way into the basilica to catch a
OL,10,Fglimpse of Francis's body, which is
OL,11,Flaid out in a simple, open coffin. Ed
OL,12,Fhopes to be able to file past, but
OL,13,Fknows it may not be possible due to
OL,14,Fthe huge crowds.
OL,16,F"I know that I will be there on
OL,17,FSaturday morning for his funeral mass,
OL,18,Fand just the honour to be there to
OL,19,Fgive thanks to God for his life and
OL,20,Fhow much that has meant to so many of
OL,21,Fus will be a great blessing for me."
