OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,FEd did get to meet Pope Francis after
OL,7,Fa member of the Jewish Community in
OL,8,FBelfast told him she was going to a
OL,9,Fprivate audience at a conference, the
OL,10,FInternational Council of Christians
OL,11,Fand Jews. He was able to go along and
OL,12,Fjoin the 150 strong delegation, and
OL,13,Fdid get a handshake and a photo.
OL,15,F"I was able to bring greetings from
OL,16,Fthe Redemptorist community here and
OL,17,Fjust to thank him personally for all
OL,18,Fthat he has meant to me," he said.
