OL,6,FEd will now head to Rome to share his
OL,7,Fgratitude once again, this time with
OL,8,Fmillions of others sharing the same
OL,9,Fsentiment.
OL,11,FIn doing do he will witness a papal
OL,12,Ffuneral like none before, as Francis
OL,13,Fsaid no to a lot of the traditional
OL,14,Fpomp and ceremony. He left
OL,15,Finstructions in which he asked to be
OL,16,Fburied in a simple underground tomb in
OL,17,FRome's papal basilica of Saint Mary
OL,18,FMajor.
