OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,FIn his will, he wrote: "I have always
OL,7,Fentrusted my life and priestly and
OL,8,Fepiscopal ministry to the Mother of
OL,9,FOur Lord, Mary Most Holy.
OL,11,F"Therefore, I ask that my mortal
OL,12,Fremains rest, awaiting the day of
OL,13,Fresurrection, in the Papal Basilica of
OL,14,FSaint Mary Major.
OL,16,F"I wish that my final earthly journey
OL,17,Fconclude precisely in this ancient
OL,18,FMarian shrine, where I go to pray at
OL,19,Fthe beginning and end of every
OL,20,FApostolic Journey...
