OL,3,CBelfast peace-builder Vatican bound to
OL,4,Csay 'goodbye with much gratitude'
OL,6,F"I ask that my tomb be prepared in the
OL,7,Fburial niche in the side nave between
OL,8,Fthe Pauline Chapel and the Sforza
OL,9,FChapel of the aforementioned Papal
OL,10,FBasilica, as indicated in the enclosed
OL,11,Fplan.
OL,13,F"The tomb should be in the ground;
OL,14,Fsimple, without particular
OL,15,Fornamentation, and bearing only the
OL,16,Finscription: Franciscus."
